<para style="q1">

<verse number="21" style="v" />Blessed be Yahweh,</para>

<para style="q1">for he showed me his marvelous covenant faithfulness when I was in a beseiged city.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="22" style="v" />Though I said in my haste,</para>

<para style="q1">"I am cut off from your eyes,"</para>

<para style="q1">yet you heard my plea for help</para>

<para style="q1">when I cried to you.</para>
